                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 16,
                        "end": 18
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "And he shall be like a tree planted by the rivers of water, that bringeth forth his fruit in his season; his leaf also shall not wither; and whatsoever he doeth shall prosper.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "Jer. 17:8 (7\u20138).",
                        "start": 23,
                        "end": 27
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "Gen. 39:3 (2\u20133); Mosiah 1:7; Alma 50:20; Hel. 12:1; D&C 9:13.",
                        "start": 167,
                        "end": 174
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "The ungodly are not so: but are like the chaff which the wind driveth away.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "Job 21:18 (17\u201318); Ps. 83:13 (2, 13); Hosea 13:3 (1\u20134); Morm. 5:16 (16\u201318).",
